{"tid":424213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又係90後！90後男子襲警被捕！","createTime":"2017-10-04T13:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T14:26:22.000Z","uid":28031,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"643be1a335aa51a453072fecf0d6443a784480c6","tid":424213,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:20:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">93歲</span></span>翁襲警被捕！上午11時許，姓洪（93歲）老翁於輕鐵元朗康樂路站附近過馬路時，疑因貪方便「衝紅燈」，一名警員巡經見狀，遂上前將他截停及票控，期間有人突然情緒激動揮拳襲擊警員。警員猝不及防，臉及手受傷，清醒送博愛醫院治理。老翁涉嫌襲警被捕，案件交元朗警區刑事調查隊跟進。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">90後可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"f4b9ece80390844a4838a5dfe86099e69400fbba","tid":424213,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:23:39.000Z","msg":"清醒送博愛醫院治理<br />\n<br />\n又一星期SL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b978b1a2c8a49d27a4c0048de650d1886858351","tid":424213,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:25:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清醒送博愛醫院治理<br />\n<br />\n又一星期SL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n90後目無法紀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197e0af26ce58d898b7b07c607aac75a4b14e99e","tid":424213,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:35:50.000Z","msg":"暴龍哥：九十後九十後，九十歲後呀，燒片"},{"pid":"0fd26c31212e28ce38c74c339f33b3e5049675be","tid":424213,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:53:09.000Z","msg":"而家啲九十後真係無法無天<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f51c99ce55061a8d59d9414dc189b865a7a6a87e","tid":424213,"uid":10126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:55:48.000Z","msg":"比個90幾歲阿伯打到送院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad